Appendix: 
Table: The mapping of permissions of three characters to octal/decimal 
Permissions Binary Octal/Decimal 
--- 000 0 
--x 001 1 
-w- 010 2 
-wx 011 3 
r-- 100 4 
r-x 101 5 
rw- 110 6 

 
